{"tid":1063244,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃之鋒：但我相信，總要有人擔當衝撞體制的角色","createTime":"2019-03-15T15:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T16:23:28.000Z","uid":5843,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2228009bda86411032c81db628742e77f5a13c82","tid":1063244,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ntdimg.com/pic/2014/10-1/p5411579a792944719.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fntdimg.com%2Fpic%2F2014%2F10-1%2Fp5411579a792944719.jpg&h=f11a6d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因不足廿日後有案件判刑，思前想後選擇了缺席是次行動，隔著螢幕看著示威現場，還是相當忐忑不安。<br />\n<br />\n在政治低潮裡，仍願意擔當行動者，實在難能可貴，尤其是有新血願意參與其中，九人當中有五人才不過是首次被捕。<br />\n<br />\n也許體制不因我們的行動而頓時會有轉變，但我相信，總要有人擔當衝撞體制的角色，謝謝你們。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K41ywtY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK41ywtY.png&h=183205ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd8824949cabd7f43d7c845cf7fd0466507ebb37","tid":1063244,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T16:09:30.000Z","msg":"u no gun<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a19e0670c4aa7d966c52f4ba30d26b2f3f6223","tid":1063244,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd8824949cabd7f43d7c845cf7fd0466507ebb37","tid":1063244,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T16:09:30.000Z","msg":"u no gun<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T16:23:28.000Z","msg":"一開live:圍堵立法會<br />\n畀人拉：得9條友點圍堵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}